name: MILSKIL PTY LTD
about: MILSKIL PTY LTD is a 100% Australian-owned company specializing in high-end operational capability and air warfare training. With over 20 years of experience, MILSKIL serves military, government, and commercial clients globally. The company provides comprehensive aircrew training on advanced aircraft such as the F/A-18F Super Hornet, EA-18G Growler, and F-35 JSF, as well as maintainer training. MILSKIL is committed to delivering exceptional training programs that enhance operational readiness and safety standards. Dedicated to excellence, MILSKIL continues to set the benchmark in air warfare training.
